{"tid":734684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"製作迷你電椅虐殺蟑螂招非議　菲藝術家：牠自作自受","createTime":"2018-07-09T00:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:39:03.000Z","uid":53379,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e14760e27e61f5a20414e9b90d6a2b0493d6c0e7","tid":734684,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>製作迷你電椅虐殺蟑螂招非議　菲藝術家：牠自作自受 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180707/s00005/828f830dd24d93a57f0f1338774fbc73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180707%2Fs00005%2F828f830dd24d93a57f0f1338774fbc73.jpg&h=28d44364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在家裏若見到蟑螂，不少人都毫不猶疑拿起拖鞋拍死牠，又或嚇得跑到老遠。不過，菲律賓有人特意為蟑螂打造迷你電椅，使闖進其家的蟑螂在痛苦中死去，做法惹來批評。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓帕西市的雕塑家圖瓦森（Gabriel Tuazon），周三（4日）晚在家中見到一隻蟑螂。圖瓦森沒有趕牠走，或直接將其置諸死地，反而花2小時，用小木條、電線、燈泡製作了一張蟑螂專用的迷你電椅。<br />\n<br />\n圖瓦森將蟑螂綁在椅子上，再拍片記錄蟑螂死去的過程。本來蟑螂受外界刺激會作出反應，但一駁上電源，牠掙扎了幾下，之後就不再動了。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評圖瓦森虐待動物，做法不能接受。不過圖瓦森似乎不感後悔，稱自己因天氣熱而開窗，蟑螂不應趁機進入屋內，一切是蟑螂自作自受。<br />\n<br />\n（英國都市日報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00005/1530940162773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00005%2F1530940162773&d=%2BTNpM2DZD3j0HRxZHuxcIAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=30bf9b4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00005%2F1530940162773&h=5dc8bca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00005/1530940162773</a>"},{"pid":"6befd48be508fbb2e0b922dcd5f79978bfeecea5","tid":734684,"uid":137896,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"比張電椅我我都唔敢捉隻強啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30faa5fd246e77c8409db19ed12e3cb